data.description: Welcome home to the community of Mountain's Edge! This two story, two car garage, three bedroom, three bathroom home features, open floor plan downstairs. The large kitchen has a pantry and is open to the living room with plenty of windows for natural light. Upstairs is the master bedroom with a private master bathroom / separate tub & shower, dual sinks, large walk in closet. The laundry room and two other bedrooms and another full size bathroom are also upstairs. Backyard with a patio cover.
